g.text: Cuno: "Hold up, piggo. There's something you gotta understand about the Cuno first." He drags his sleeve across his nose. "Cuno's gotta protect the Cuno name."
Jump to: [Esprit de Corps: "If an assault were launched on this..."]
Cuno: "Listen up, pig! Cuno's gonna scram now." He rubs his hands together.
Cuno: "The gimps out there ain't gonna think we a thing. Cuno will follow you, but don't expect anything *extra* okay, pig? Cuno's silent, like a fucking vegetable."
Tutorial Agent: Cuno will rejoin your party later.
Kim Kitsuragi: As you approach the door leading out of the hostel, the bespectacled man in an orange bomber jacket turns to you:
Cuno: "So yeah -- see you on the seafort island. Try not to get shot or drunk again. Cuno's counting on your ass."
Cuno: "And don't forget about that bitch's window. Scope that shit. Cop Cuno's telling you, that's the break in the case."
Cuno: "See you on the seafort island -- try not to get shot again or drunk or shit. Cuno's counting on you."
Kim Kitsuragi: "Excuse me... I think you may be the person I've been waiting for." He narrows his eyes and extends his hand in greeting.

Cuno: "Cuno's gonna scram now." He rubs his hands together. "Can't be seen with pigs. Can't shit on Cuno's good name."
